snippet.title: Amber Heard's Camp Attacking and Twisting Words of Supporters of JD on Social Media
snippet.description:
Amber Heard has been tripling down in her attacks of those who would support her ex-husband Johnny Depp in their on-going legal battle on social media. 

It's important to point out that never has any of his camp attacked every day people like you and I and yet she has employed media people to smear real DV survivors and supporters of him because they see the truth. 

It is also important to point out that they are using a tactic that is OFTEN used in the media when they want to spin a life and that is something called Logical Fallacies. https://yourlogicalfallacyis.com/ You would benefit from studying the different types of fallacies and how they are used to fool the public, quite easily.
